assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: SBT Ultrasonic Technology Co.,Ltd. engages in the research, development, manufacturing, and sale ultrasonic products for metal testing and ultrasonic solutions. The company offers products, such as ultrasonic metal welding that helps welding system; real-time welding quality detection system, smart welding and detection combination system; ODM/OEM horns and bottom molds; tapered bar ultrasonic welding system, full-wave ultrasonic welding system, and ultrasonic welding system for auto wire harness and IGBT power module terminals; tire rubber industry application, check and detect; and ultrasonic welding for mask production. It also provides ultrasonic side cutting systems, ultrasonic straight cutting systems, 40k cutting systems, 20k cutting systems, cutting assembly modification and custom-made horns, X-rayor detection and auto-rejection systems, CCD visual inspection systems for the tire and rubber industry, pharmaceutical metal detectors, vertical fall metal detectors, pipeline metal detectors, conveyorized metal detector systems, automatic metal detectors, and metal testing machine heads. It serves lithium-ion battery production, tire rubber cutting, and food and pharmaceutical detection industries. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Shanghai, China.
